types.description:
Errors messages and codes mapped to
fields or non fields errors.
Example:
{
    field_name: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ],
    other_field: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ],
    nonFieldErrors: [
        {
            "message": "error message",
            "code": "error_code"
        }
    ]
}
